{"tid":594944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]鄭家純家被爆竊　幸無失身僅失金","createTime":"2018-03-16T09:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T01:15:54.000Z","uid":26769,"like":125,"dislike":322,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"285edbb4e6fe5cf752185e26ce6f83daaf12ae4b","tid":594944,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160808/55469425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160808%2F55469425&d=uvnUwBOD0%2FcZEeC6XjBEZJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d8580520\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160808%2F55469425&h=14a23c88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160808/55469425</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160808/large/1470625473_1f57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160808%2Flarge%2F1470625473_1f57.jpg&h=1267b354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界發展前主席鄭裕彤家族持有的淺水灣道12號獨立屋，被賊人入屋爆竊。彤叔長子、新世界主席鄭家純，今早10時25分返回獨立屋了解情況。他離開大宅前說：「少意思，損失一啲金器，喺咁簡單，冇乜特別，普通嘢，當時有屋企人喺屋企，但係鎖晒門，唔知發生咩事，所以冇受驚，個賊入唔到房，只係喺走廊攞走少少嘢，會加強保安。」"},{"pid":"abee71dfcf9775beb8af77c1a9fb0c1fde838771","tid":594944,"uid":2419,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c631fe8143cce161c3cd9492edbf63e450d4dc08","tid":594944,"uid":33864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d804620508d0ad2689882b6931ff227c1cab24","tid":594944,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"Old news is s